<div><head>楚竹書八《昔者君老》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.2">君子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.3">昔者君老，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.4">太子朝君，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.5">君之母弟是相。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.6">太子昃聽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.7">庶叩，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.8">叩進。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.9">太子前之母弟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.10">母弟遜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.11">退，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.12">前之太子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.13">再三，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.14">然後並聽之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.15">太子母弟<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.16">至命於閤門，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.17">以告寺人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.18">寺人入告于君，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.19">君曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.20">召之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.21">太子入見，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.22">如祭祀之事<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.23">爾司，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.24">各恭爾事，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.25">發命不斁。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.26">君卒。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.27">太子乃亡聞、亡聽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.28">不聞不令，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.29">唯哀悲是思，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.30">唯邦之大務是敬。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.31">能事其親。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.32">君子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.33">子省，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.34">蓋喜於內，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.35">不見於外；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.36">喜於外，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.37">不見於內。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.38">慍於外，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.39">不見於內。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.40">慍於內，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.41">不見於外。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.42">內言不以出，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.43">外言不以入。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4536_CHANT_001-1a.44">舉媺廢惡<lb/></seg>
</p>
